name: Northeast Corridor: New York - Trenton
location: New York City, New York - Trenton, New Jersey

routeFacts.name: Northeast Corridor: New York - Trenton
routeFacts.description: Experience the thrill of railroading along the busling Northeast Corridor, the United States' busiest rail corridor. The Northeast Corridor is home to several passenger rail operators and even some freight lines. The NEC: New York - Trenton DLC puts you in control of Amtrak and NJ Transit passenger trains on a bustling timetable that serves 11 million passengers annually.
routeInfo: In this DLC, players will have access to a number of different locomotives, including the Amtrak ACS-64 and NJ Transit ALP-45DP, allowing them to experience the different trains that run along the Northeast Corridor. The game features a detailed recreation of the route, including accurate train schedules, realistic weather conditions, and intricate train signaling systems. Players will have the opportunity to control trains, navigate busy stations, and experience the hustle and bustle of the Northeast Corridor in a way that only a simulation can provide.
